# AlignSynch Project Structure

## Tech Stack
- **Next.js 15** with App Router
- **React 19** with latest features
- **TypeScript** for type safety
- **Tailwind CSS** for styling
- **ShadCN UI** components
- **Drizzle ORM** for database
- **PostgreSQL** database
- **BetterAuth** for authentication

## Key Directories
- `app/` - Next.js App Router pages and layouts
- `components/` - Reusable React components
- `lib/` - Utility functions and configurations
- `public/` - Static assets
- `styles/` - Global CSS styles

## Entry Points
- Main app entry: [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx)
- Root layout: [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx)
- Database schema: [lib/db/schema.ts](mdc:lib/db/schema.ts)
- Environment config: [env.local.template](mdc:env.local.template)